421
00:33:40,700 --> 00:33:42,800
<i>This is Guixu.</i>

422
00:33:42,800 --> 00:33:45,400
<i>It looks like this.</i>

423
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:50,200
<i>If one day, Guixu breaks the seal, the whole world will be destroyed.</i>

424
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:54,300
<i>Xiao Feichi, you are my only friend in the Land of Mystery.</i>

425
00:33:54,300 --> 00:33:59,900
<i>If one day, Guixu really shows an anomaly, you need to lead an army to guard the Heavenly Southern Gate.</i>

426
00:33:59,900 --> 00:34:03,400
<i>Then go help the people who are hurt.</i>

427
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:05,900
<i>This is the Heavenly Southern Gate.</i>

428
00:34:13,400 --> 00:34:15,000
<i>Do you understand?</i>

429
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:17,400
<i>What about you then?</i>

430
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:19,000
<i>Then,</i>

431
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:24,400
<i>I guess I'll be dead like my master.</i>

432
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:32,900
<i>There is really someone so silly</i>
<i>[Xuanshang]</i>

433
00:34:32,900 --> 00:34:36,500
