434
00:34:36,500 --> 00:34:43,930
<i>Heartless Shaodian, did you arrange your own death quietly in such a lonesome place?</i>

435
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:52,400
You have her now.

436
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:53,900
- Yes.
- Yes.

437
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:56,600
Come with me.

438
00:35:21,300 --> 00:35:23,800
Princess, this is it.

439
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:25,400
Please.

440
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:36,200
This is the Cave of Haunted Souls?

441
00:35:36,200 --> 00:35:38,200
<i>Yes, yes.</i>

442
00:35:38,200 --> 00:35:40,600
Why are you so afraid of me?

443
00:35:40,600 --> 00:35:42,100
I am the prisoner.

444
00:35:42,100 --> 00:35:44,200
P-Princess, we aren't allowed to be afraid.

445
00:35:44,200 --> 00:35:46,600
I am not afraid.

446
00:35:46,600 --> 00:35:47,600
Yes, right.

447
00:35:47,600 --> 00:35:49,100
Okay, then you can go.

448
00:35:49,100 --> 00:35:50,700
