Third Prince said, anyone who upsets the princess shall be beheaded.

452
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:59,600
One head will be worth one hundred Void Coins.

453
00:35:59,600 --> 00:36:00,700
So listen up.

454
00:36:00,700 --> 00:36:05,100
Let's take a few more heads, otherwise, we won't have enough money for our men.

455
00:36:05,100 --> 00:36:06,800
The princess seems unhappy.

456
00:36:06,800 --> 00:36:08,200
Is she scared by that guy?

457
00:36:08,200 --> 00:36:10,000
Let's kill him first.

458
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:11,300
Please stop crying.

459
00:36:11,300 --> 00:36:13,000
- Just stand up first.
<i>- Princess.</i>

460
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:16,200
Princess. Please.

461
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:40,400
After we return, I will ask royal father to marry Tan Tan to me.

462
00:37:26,600 --> 00:37:29,400
Sir, we should set off.

463
00:37:29,400 --> 00:37:31,200
Take the army and go without me.

464
00:37:31,200 --> 00:37:33,600
I will go to Cave of Haunted Souls first.

465
00:37:35,300 --> 00:37:37,300
I have arranged everything there.

466
00:37:37,300 --> 00:37:38,500
This war is special.

467
00:37:38,500 --> 00:37:40,300
I suggest we set off right away.

468
00:37:40,300 --> 00:37:44,800
It is because this war is special that I have to go talk to her before I leave.

469
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:46,300
What's there to talk about?

470
00:37:46,300 --> 00:37:49,300
As long as we win, the princess will surely be your...

471
00:37:49,300 --> 00:37:51,500
What if Wu Dai or Dingyun wins?

472
00:37:51,500 --> 00:37:55,400
Do I just watch her marry Wu Dai or Dingyun?

473
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:58,800
There's something I have to tell her.

474
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:00,000
Have some faith in yourself.

475
00:38:00,000 --> 00:38:02,200
Sir. Wait. Sir.

476
00:38:02,200 --> 00:38:03,800
Sir!

477
00:38:08,300 --> 00:38:10,700
- Good.
- Nice. Nice.

478
00:38:10,700 --> 00:38:13,000
- Higher.
- Good.

479
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:14,300
Higher. Higher.

480
00:38:14,300 --> 00:38:16,600
Right. Right.

481
00:38:16,600 --> 00:38:18,600
The princess isn't laughing.

482
00:38:22,200 --> 00:38:24,800
Choke me. Choke me. Do it.

483
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:30,000
I laid an egg.

484
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:31,600
The princess laughed.

485
00:38:31,600 --> 00:38:33,400
How about we put on a play for you?

486
00:38:33,400 --> 00:38:35,100
Princess, let me lay another egg for you.

487
00:38:35,100 --> 00:38:36,200
I'll lay another one for you.

488
00:38:36,200 --> 00:38:37,900
Hold on.

489
00:38:37,900 --> 00:38:39,600
I appreciate your kind gesture.

490
00:38:39,600 --> 00:38:43,500
But ever since I came into Cave of Haunted Souls, I have watched many of your shows.

491
00:38:43,500 --> 00:38:45,000
I am a bit tired now.

492
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:49,200
Princess, we will leave you alone then.

493
00:38:49,200 --> 00:38:51,000
If you need anything, Princess...

494
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:54,600
I will tell you. I promise.

495
00:38:54,600 --> 00:38:56,900
<i>We'll get going.</i>

496
00:38:57,400 --> 00:38:59,200
Take our stuff. Take it.

497
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:01,500
Come on. Come.

